headline: Duke Energy helps communities across Ohio and Kentucky prepare sites to bring local investment, jobs
summary: Duke Energy selected three properties in Southwest Ohio and Northern Kentucky for inclusion in its 2025 Site Readiness Program, which prepares high-potential business and industrial sites for economic development investments and markets them nationwide to companies looking to start, expand or relocate their operations.
